{
  "index": 2,
  "title": "The Mechanics of Greenhouse Emissions",
  "html": "\n  <section class=\"slide\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; min-height: 100vh; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; padding: 2rem; background-color: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: var(--font-body);\">\n  <style>\n    .slide-content {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n      gap: 3rem;\n      max-width: 90vw;\n      align-items: start;\n    }\n    .slide-header {\n      grid-column: 1 / -1;\n      text-align: left;\n      margin-bottom: 2rem;\n    }\n    .slide-title {\n      font-family: var(--font-head);\n      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);\n      color: var(--text);\n      margin: 0;\n      border-left: 8px solid var(--accent);\n      padding-left: 1.5rem;\n    }\n    .mechanism-diagram {\n      background: var(--surface);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: 1rem;\n      padding: 2rem;\n      position: relative;\n      overflow: hidden;\n      box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--accent-glow);\n    }\n    .process-step {\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      gap: 1rem;\n      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n      opacity: 0;\n      transform: translateX(-20px);\n      transition: all 0.5s ease;\n    }\n    .process-step.reveal {\n      opacity: 1;\n      transform: translateX(0);\n      transition-delay: var(--delay);\n    }\n    .step-number {\n      background: var(--accent);\n      color: var(--bg);\n      width: 2rem;\n      height: 2rem;\n      border-radius: 50%;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      font-weight: bold;\n      flex-shrink: 0;\n    }\n    .sources-grid {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n      gap: 1rem;\n      margin-top: 2rem;\n    }\n    .source-card {\n      background: var(--surface);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      padding: 1.5rem;\n      border-radius: 0.5rem;\n      transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n    }\n    .source-card:hover {\n      transform: translateY(-5px);\n      border-color: var(--accent);\n    }\n    .source-card h4 {\n      margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;\n      color: var(--accent);\n      font-family: var(--font-head);\n    }\n    .source-card p {\n      font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.2vw, 1.1rem);\n      color: var(--text-muted);\n      margin: 0;\n    }\n    .correlation-alert {\n      margin-top: 2rem;\n      padding: 1rem;\n      background: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.1);\n      border-left: 4px solid #ff4444;\n      font-style: italic;\n      color: var(--text-muted);\n      font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.2vw, 1.1rem);\n    }\n    .visual-layer {\n      position: absolute;\n      top: 0; right: 0;\n      width: 100px; height: 100px;\n      background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--accent-glow) 0%, transparent 70%);\n      opacity: 0.3;\n    }\n  </style>\n\n  <div class=\"slide-content\">\n    <header class=\"slide-header\">\n      <h1 class=\"slide-title\">The Mechanics of Greenhouse Emissions</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"mechanism-diagram\">\n      <div class=\"visual-layer\"></div>\n      <h3 style=\"color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-family: var(--font-head);\">The Greenhouse Process</h3>\n      \n      <div class=\"process-step reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.2s\">\n        <div class=\"step-number\">1</div>\n        <div><strong>Solar Radiation:</strong> High-energy shortwave light enters the atmosphere.</div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"process-step reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.4s\">\n        <div class=\"step-number\">2</div>\n        <div><strong>Surface Absorption:</strong> The Earth absorbs energy and re-emits it as infrared heat.</div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"process-step reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.6s\">\n        <div class=\"step-number\">3</div>\n        <div><strong>Atmospheric Trapping:</strong> GHGs absorb this heat, preventing it from escaping to space.</div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"process-step reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.8s\">\n        <div class=\"step-number\">4</div>\n        <div><strong>Thermal Feedback:</strong> Trapped heat increases surface and atmospheric temperature.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"details-col\">\n      <h3 style=\"color: var(--text); font-family: var(--font-head); margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Primary Forcing Agents</h3>\n      <div class=\"sources-grid\">\n        <div class=\"source-card reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 1s\">\n          <h4>CO₂</h4>\n          <p>Fossil fuel combustion, deforestation, and industrial cement production.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"source-card reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 1.2s\">\n          <h4>CH₄</h4>\n          <p>Agriculture (livestock), landfill decomposition, and natural gas leaks.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"correlation-alert reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 1.4s\">\n        <strong>Linear Correlation:</strong> Historical data shows a direct, positive correlation between atmospheric CO₂ concentrations and global mean temperature anomalies.\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  \n</section>\n  \n\n\n  ",
